Name: Cyber Miner
About the game: Cyber Miner is a roguelite flappy game with endless progression. Pick a cube character, each with unique abilities, complete an obstacle run with assistance of various power-ups and unlock the next level... Which is the same level you just done, but harder. Repeat indefinitely or at least until you get bored of it.
